722710f-a.title: Manhattan: Riverside Drive - 80th Street (West)
722710f-a.text:
Riverside Drive, north from West 80th Street, showing the transitional aspects of this marginal thoroughfare. In the foreground is one of the last scuatters shacks. The row of buildings at the tight is at the S. E. corner of West 82nd Street.
About 189S
Gift of Urbrock Collection
